<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森走进体育馆时，雪莉老师正在贴公告。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面写着：为自由小学捐赠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22939</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公告下面有几个空箱子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生什么事了？” 贾森问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “上周的雷雨天让一所小学烧毁了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们几乎失去了他们所有的东西！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39408</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>书、铅笔……现在他们需要很多帮助。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52477</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森从口袋里拿出一个新的橡皮擦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给您。” 他说，“这是我们的第一个捐赠物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “谢谢你，贾森。你真善良。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “弗里克老师今天也跟我们说了。” 伊坦说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我明天要把我的旧计算器带过来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78475</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “不管捐什么，孩子们都会喜欢的。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们等会儿再说这件事吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “现在围上围裙！我们要做苹果酱松饼。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，我们需要把干食材混合起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比，让伊坦看看我们是怎么做的吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一杯半面粉。” 波比念出黑板上的内容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “发酵粉和小苏打。” 贾森继续说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “半茶匙盐。” 尼娜接着念。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家看着伊坦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“肉桂！” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “很好！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，我们把湿食材混合起来。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “融化的黄油。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “三分之二杯红糖。” 波比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“混合好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “两个鸡蛋。” 贾森边说边打鸡蛋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一杯半苹果酱。” 伊坦念道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们搅拌干食材和湿食材。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只要稍微搅拌就可以，搅拌太多了反而不好。” 雪莉老师告诉大家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我会把湿食材放进干食材的碗里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦，你来搅拌。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “莉琪有时爱指挥别人。” 波比对伊坦说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但她很善良。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家把彩色的纸杯放进松饼烤盘里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们把面糊倒进去。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要倒太满。松饼在烤箱里会膨胀。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “要烤多久呢？” 莉琪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “二十分钟。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236079</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森又在想自由小学的孩子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“自由小学的孩子们也有课后活动班吗？” 他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250074</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在学校修复之前，他们会在市政厅里活动。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “那他们也需要捐赠吗？” 贾森问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “是的。他们失去了大部分的手工材料和烹饪工具。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一段时间内会很困难。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “要是我们能做点其他事情就好了。” 贾森想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“松饼做好了！” 莉琪大喊。她跑到烤箱旁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等凉一点就可以吃了。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等！别吃！” 贾森突然说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296678</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有一个想法！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我们应该把松饼送给自由小学的课后活动班！” 贾森说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以把它叫作课后苹果酱松饼！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好想法！” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以明天送过去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>   “好！” 贾森欢呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帮助别人的感觉真好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>